data.description: Welcome to your new home in Lake Shore Estates, where tranquility meets convenience! This charming 3 bed/2 bath single story home sits on a corner lot measuring slightly over 1 acre and features an expansive greenbelt. This home offers an open floor plan, gorgeous high ceilings, separate dining, stunning stone veneer fireplace, new LVP flooring throughout, new ceiling fans and light fixtures, and lots of storage space with newly installed organization systems! Some of the upgrades include new water heater, new dishwasher, new water softener, USB outlets, new doors & hardware, fresh paint throughout, and an exterior security camera system. Don't miss your chance to make this exceptional home yours today! Schedule your showing and discover the perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and natural beauty!
